node.text:
I tried @blessedprotein in the flavor Salted Carmel and was very impressed how yummy it tastes!
•
Blessed protein is designed to help with any goal in mind. Protein is essential to give your muscles the recovery after a hard workout. All while tasting good! Blessed is a plant based protein that is gluten free, dairy free, & soy free. 
Use code LESH10 to save $ off your order on www.ehplabs.com!
